- workload

- level of theory / math

I'm really really interested in both, and I can't freaking choose for the life of me whether 182 would be more interesting because it's such a good pairing with 189 (and also deep learning!11!1), or whether 191 would be more interesting because it's q u a n t u m c o m p u t i n g and I love quantum computing.
